---
title: Smart Shawarma Spiced Beef Patties with Spinach Salad and Couscous
description: Beef patties are mixed with big flavour makers like shallots and Shawarma Spice Blend before being pan-fried to juicy perfection in this recipe. Aromatic couscous and zingy garlic sauce ensure you don't sacrifice taste for calorie- and carb-consciousness.
